# ── Zag language classification (interim) ────────────────────────────────────
# GitHub does not know "Zag" until github-linguist/linguist PR #8041 merges.
# Until then, classify .zag as Zig for syntax highlighting on github.com.
*.zag linguist-language=Zig linguist-detectable

# ── Generated / support files (keep language stats on .zag sources) ───────────
*.zag.c linguist-generated
zag-poc/selfhost/native/znc.zag.c linguist-generated
zag-poc/tests/stdlib/*.zag.c linguist-generated

editors/** linguist-vendored
zag-poc/std/runtime.c linguist-vendored